_sText:
This map was originally created for the 2008 Joe.To Abstract Mappack, which can be found here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/58046

Depending on your graphics settings, certain things in this map may or may not appear as was intended. So be sure to keep that in mind. Certain things, like the art gallery bombsite for example, will NOT look right on DX level 8.1 or lower.

In this map, there are secrets, traps, absurdity and other assorted crazyness. So be on your guard!

As usual, special thanks go out to the joe.to community, and all who gave me very useful tips and criticism to help make this map better. You guys should have seen my original version. I mean, the FIRST, FIRST one before I deleted entire rooms and started over. Horrible.

Enjoy!
